tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE support_tickets (
  ticket_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  ticket_description TEXT,
  agent_id INT,
  expertise_level INT,
  workload INT,
  status VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE SupportTickets (
   ticket_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   description TEXT,
   status VARCHAR(50),
   agent_id INT,
   created_at TIMESTAMP
);
